trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to append to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" />.
Appends the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object to the end of the collection.
Occurs when the collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects is changed.

The <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Changed> event occurs when the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Add%2A> method, the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Remove%2A> method, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Clear%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Changed>就會發生事件時<xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Add%2A>方法，<xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Remove%2A>方法，或<xref:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.Clear%2A>方法呼叫。

trans-unit.source: Removes all the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects from the collection.
The <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to locate in the collection.
Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> collection contains a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object.
<see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.

Copies all the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index in the target array.
The zero-based array that receives the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects copied from the collection.
The position in the target array at which the array starts receiving the copied items.

Copies all the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index in the target array.
The zero-based array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects that receives the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects copied from the collection.
The position in the target array at which the array starts receiving the copied items.

Copies all the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects from the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> collection to a one-dimensional array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects, starting at the specified index in the target array.
Gets the number of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> collection.
The number of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" />.
Returns an <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />-implemented object that can be used to iterate through the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects in the collection.

An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" />-implemented object that contains all the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" />.
Gets a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> objects in the collection can be modified.
<see langword="false" /> in all cases.
Gets a value indicating whether access to the collection is synchronized (thread safe).
<see langword="false" /> in all cases.
The <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to retrieve.
Gets an <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object from the collection with the specified <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" /> value.
An <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> with the specified <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" />.
Removes the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object from the collection.
The <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object from the collection.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object from the collection.
The <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding.PropertyName" /> of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to remove from the collection.

<see langword="true" /> to add the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> to the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection.RemovedBindings" /> collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
Removes the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBinding" /> object from the collection.
Gets a collection of strings representing the names of bindings that have been removed.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" /> containing the names of bindings that have been removed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Collections.ICollection" />含有已移除的繫結的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets an object that can be used to synchronize access to the collection.
An <see cref="T:System.Object" /> that can be used to synchronize access to the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Object" />，可用於同步處理 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.ExpressionBindingCollection" /> 的存取。
